

building good UI for login, sign-up, and landing pages.


Recommended Books for UI Design & Frontend Development

“Don’t Make Me Think” by Steve Krug
A classic on user experience design, clear and practical.

“Refactoring UI” by Adam Wathan & Steve Schoger
Great for developers who want to learn beautiful UI design principles.

“Designing Interfaces” by Jenifer Tidwell
Comprehensive guide to UI patterns and best practices.

“JavaScript and Vue.js: Up and Running” by Callum Macrae
Hands-on Vue.js book with practical UI examples.

